Rating: 4
I gave this 4 forks because it's so, so simple. It's super fast. It's presents very well and it's so classically tasty. (butter, potatoes, salt and parsley, right?). I used larger pink-skinned potatoes. I will use smaller ones next time. Also...make sure you use a metal backing pan to get that gorgeous crispy, brown color and texture on the bottom. My glass baking pan did not yield the same result.

